<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.7.5">
<l>meṉṟa pēḻvāy vāḷeyiṟṟōrk kōḷari yāyavuṇaṉ</l>
<l>poṉṟa vākam vaḷḷukirāl pōḻntapu ṉitaṉiṭam</l>
<l>niṉṟa centī moṇṭucūṟai nīḷvicum pūṭiriya</l>
<l>ceṉṟu kāṇṭaṟ kariyakōyil ciṅkavēḷ kuṉṟamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The place of the pure one, who split with his sharp claws the chest</l>
<l rend="indent">so the demon died,</l>
<l>Becoming a fierce lion with sword[-like] teeth</l>
<l rend="indent">and a cavernous mouth that gnawed,</l>
<l>Is Lion-Man Mountain, the temple difficult to discern</l>
<l rend="indent">as whirlwinds arrive</l>
<l>And, scooping up [ever] present crimson sparks,</l>
<l rend="indent">so they flee into the high heavens.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
